title: Bug 109350 - Output parameter should display in the data set dialog.
OB: While on the query result page, no data is returned. The actual result is that the output parameter should display in the edit data set dialog.
SR:
To reproduce this issue:
1. Open the query result page.
2. Execute a query that should return data.
3. Check the edit data set dialog to verify if the output parameter is displayed correctly.
